window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Free from those who would seek to make him their pawn, Kyle is now able to seek his own destiny. </b></p> <p>His team is shaping up around him, but becoming divine has given him a larger view of things.</p> <p>He never asked for any of this but can he turn his back on all of creation? That may very well be what is at stake. His relationship issues may just have to take a backseat.</p> <p>But let his foes beware, if a team isn't enough then the war god shall raise an army.</p>"; 
